title: Global Day of Coderetreat 2015 - Omaha, NE, USA
description:
Ready to hone your craft? Then come to Omaha's code retreat! This is a free, one-day event where like minded individuals can share ideas, learn, and get better. Breakfast and lunch will be provided. Bring a laptop if you can. All skill levels are welcome. Please RSVP on the EventBrite website: 
https://www.eventbrite.com/e/omaha-code-retreat-2015-tickets-9432379501
